        " اَلْأُضْحِيَّةِ فَقَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ أَنْ يُضَحَّى بِهَا »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3060 - Abu Ja'far (as) was asked about an old animal whose front teeth have fallen out. Is it permissible for sacrifice?\nImam (as) replied: \"There is no harm in sacrificing it.\""
        ]
